==Description==
The '''Helix Fossil''' is a type of [[Fossils|Fossil]].

==Details==
When a '''Helix Fossil''' is placed in the [[Pokémon Day Care]], it hatches into an Omanyte.

==Mine Layout==
The Helix Fossil appears in the Underground as a 4x4 sized object.<br><br>
